            "assertion": "assert methodResultID == (int)((this).hashCode() + ((List<Object>)(this)).edges().stream().mapToInt(e -> e.hashCode()).sum());",
            "description": "the hash code value must be the sum of the hash codes of vertices and edges in the graph, based on graph topology and edges weights"
